name: Crab
long-desc: An example of one of the most popular marine designs ever conceived by nature. All was once and will eventually return to crab.

name: Platinum Fish
short-desc: A shiny, silvery streak in the river.
long-desc: The domestication of the long-adored Goldfish left a gap for other organisms to display materialistic value. Eventually, a fish of a higher tier emerged and took its place as the king of small bodies of water.

name: Pufferfish
long-desc: Advanced species of fish using inflation tactics and poisonous barbs for self defense. Humans enjoy the challenge of catching and eating the creatures anyway.
